<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281189>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 8. Kanparka leki n. gen. n. sp. 2. Dorsal view of head and T 1. Scale = 1 mm. 3. Dorsal view of antennae. Scale = 0.5 mm. 4. Ventral view of forcipules and maxillae. Scale = 0.5 mm. 5. Detail of forcipular tooth plates. Scale = 250 µm. 6. Ventral view of segment 21. Scale = 0.5 mm. 7. Epipharynx. Scale = 100 µm. 8. External view of spiracle on segment 3. Scale = 100 µm. All holotype WAM T 99422 except 2, WAM T 79350, 7, WAM T 117570." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281189/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

